<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Resume Matcher Pro Trial is Ending Soon</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f7a74a;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .countdown {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f7a74a;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 2px dashed #f7a74a;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .pricing {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your Trial is Ending Soon</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>Your Resume Matcher Pro trial is about to end. We hope you've had a chance to explore all the premium features that can help boost your job search success!</p>
    
    <div class="countdown">
      Your trial ends on: <strong>{{trialEndDate}}</strong>
    </div>
    
    <p>After your trial ends, your card will be automatically charged <strong>{{currency}}{{firstBillingAmount}}</strong> to continue your subscription without interruption.</p>
    
    <div class="pricing">
      <h3>What happens next?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Your subscription will automatically continue after the trial</li>
        <li>You'll be charged {{currency}}{{firstBillingAmount}} for your first billing period</li>
        <li>You can cancel anytime before {{trialEndDate}} to avoid being charged</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <h3>Why subscribers love Resume Matcher Pro:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>80% higher interview rate</strong> with our ATS-optimized resumes</li>
      <li><strong>Save 5+ hours</strong> per job application with our tools</li>
      <li><strong>Get hired faster</strong> with personalized job matching</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Don't want to continue? No problem! You can cancel your subscription before the trial ends without being charged.</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
      <a href="{{manageBillingUrl}}" class="button" style="margin-right: 10px;">Continue My Subscription</a>
      <a href="{{manageBillingUrl}}" style="color: #777; font-size: 14px;">Cancel Subscription</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help. Just reply to this email!</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Resume Matcher Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Resume Matcher. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{manageBillingUrl}}">Manage Subscription</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings">Account Settings</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>